programme.desc: Kisah kehidupan sebuah keluarga yang berhadapan dengan masalah dan konflik diantara anak-anak dan bapa akibat perbezaan pendapat dan pandangan tentang kehidupanmasakini.

programme.title: Lag Ja Gale Ep17
programme.desc: Drama ini mengisahkan perjalanan dua individu yang berbeza latar belakang, Shiv Dhooper, seorang usahawan muda Punjabi yang berjaya, dan Ishani Kulkarni, seorang wanita dari Maharashtra yang bekerja keras untuk menyara keluarganya. Mereka dipertemukan melalui perkahwinan yang diatur untuk membantu adik-beradik mereka, walaupun mereka mempunyai pandangan hidup yang berbeza. Dalam perjalanan mereka, mereka turut menghadapi pelbagai cabaran dan konflik keluarga. Akhirnya, kisah berakhir dengan mereka membina kehidupan bersama, menandakan permulaan kisah cinta mereka yang sebenar.

programme.title: Kaaval S4 Ep11
programme.desc: Drama kepolisan mengisahkan usaha pihak polis dalam memerangi pelbagai jenis jenayah.

programme.title: Catching Shadow Ep3
programme.desc: Drama yang mengisahkan bagaimana Wen En, seorang jurutera keselamatan rangkaian di Ling Dun Network Security dibuang kerja dan memulakan syarikat keselamatannya sendiri.

programme.title: Wounded Heart Ep33
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ferit, seorang jejaka dari keluarga kaya yang dihancurkan oleh pengkhianatan orang yang dipercayainya. Dalam usaha untuk melupakan masa lalu, dia bertemu dengan Aye, seorang gadis yang ceria dan penuh semangat. Mereka membuat perjanjian yang akan mengubah hidup masing-masing, tetapi perjalanan kisah mereka dipenuhi cabaran, rahsia gelap dan dilema yang menggugat emosi. Adakah cinta mereka cukup kuat untuk mengatasi segalanya?

programme.title: Smile To Life Ep10

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Black EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Detektif Khairul Malik menyimpan sebuah rahsia, yang teman wanitanya, Aisya tidak tahu mengenainya. Perkara menjadi rumit dengan penemuan mayat dua puluh tahun, yang menggerakkan rangkaian kejadian yang membawa maut. Kehidupannya berubah secara mendadak apabila dia bertemu Sofia, gadis yang berkebolehan meramal kematian orang. Apabila dia meramal sebuah tragedi dahsyat, Sofia mendapat perhatian polis dan juga seorang keturunan usahawan insurans ulung, Lokman Nazir. Tertarik dengan bakat unik Sofia, Malik meyakinkan dia untuk bekerja bersamanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa, tetapi niat baik mereka menyebabkan tragedi. Sementara itu, penghantaran sebuah pita menyebabkan huru-hara dalam hubungan Malik dan Aisya apabila rahsia gelap Aisya mula terungkai.

programme.title: Dark Castle
programme.desc: Pasangan bahagia, Bram dan Tatia sedang berbulan madu ke St. Jean Le Vieux, Perancis. Mereka berkunjung ke Prouges, kota kecil dimana dirayakan festival musim panas. Di tengah hiruk pikuk festival, Bram dibayangi sesosok lelaki tak dikenal, sementara itu Tatia digoda oleh anak kecil yang seolah mengajaknya bermain. Tatia mengejarnya dan masuk ke dalam gang-gang kecil kota Prouges. Di salah satu gang itu Tatia diculik. Bram yang mencari Tatia pun ikut diculik.

programme.title: Skrip 7707
programme.desc: Sebuah filem antologi seram yang menghimpunkan beberapa kisah menakutkan berasaskan skrip misteri bernombor 7707. Setiap kisah menyingkap rahsia gelap yang penuh dendam, roh, dan balasan.

programme.title: Shut In
programme.desc: Seorang psikolog kanak-kanak yang menjadi janda menjalani kehidupan terpencil di kawasan luar bandar New England. Terkandas dalam ribut salji yang mematikan, dia mesti mencari cara untuk menyelamatkan seorang budak lelaki sebelum dia hilang selamanya.

programme.title: Khurafat
programme.desc: Kisah bermula dengan Johan, seorang pemuda yang bekerja sebagai Pembantu Hospital. Sudah berkahwin dan mempunyai seorang isteri bernama Aishah. programme.title: Devil's Whisper
programme.desc: Seorang remaja lelaki bercita-cita untuk menjadi seorang paderi. Tetapi dia diseksa oleh syaitan yang ingin merasukinya. Adakah kepercayaannya cukup untuk menyelamatkan jiwanya?

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Rodi bergaduh dengan pelanggan di Chow Kit selepas menipu dalam permainan jalanan. Pulang ke rumah, dia mendapati ibunya mahu melacur semula kerana terdesak wang. programme.title: Tujuh
programme.desc: Sekumpulan tujuh sahabat yang pernah terlibat dalam satu kejadian tragis bertahun lalu kembali dihantui apabila seorang demi seorang mula mati secara misteri. Dalam usaha mencari kebenaran, mereka mula menyedari bahawa dosa silam mereka tidak akan terampun dan pembalasan sedang menanti.

programme.title: SAM
programme.desc: Sam, yang pernah menjalinkan hubungan intim dengan rakan sekerjanya, mendapati bahawa bukan dirinya sahaja yang menyukai Lisa. programme.title: Heimsuchung Aka Smother
programme.desc: Apabila bapanya meninggal dunia, Michaela tinggal bersama Hanna di rumah keluarga yang kosong. Ia adalah tempat yang sesuai untuk melepaskan diri daripada semua itu dan memperbaiki hubungannya dengan anak perempuannya. Selepas kemalangan kereta bersama mereka, Michaela berhenti minum. Pengasingan luar bandar kini sepatutnya membantu. Tetapi di sini di tengah-tengah tempat, masa lalu sedang menunggu Michaela.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Rodi siasat sindiket penculikan, berdepan dilema antara tugas dan menyelamatkan Kasyorga. Reza sembunyi budak di rumah Kak Esah. Rahsia Mak Siti terbongkar. Rodi menjejak Rajoo di tengah laut.

programme.title: Boss
programme.desc: Tiga gadis bersama seorang kapten membanteras kumpulan jahat yang melanggar undang-undang. Mereka berhadapan dengan Malik yang menjalankan kegiatan pemerdagangan manusia. Pelbagai rintangan perlu mereka tempuhi apabila salah seorang anggota mereka, Clara diculik kumpulan tersebut ketika cuba menyelamatkan tahanan lain. Mereka pun memulakan misi untuk mencari Clara dan menjatuhkan kumpulan Malik.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Harry Boy
programme.desc: Kurang kasih sayang dan perhatian dari keluarga, Harry Boy mula menagih kasih di luar. Dia bertemu Julia dan mula terikut-ikut gaya hidup Julia yang bebas. Ini mendatangkan kerisauan terhadap ibu dan bapanya apabila dia mula tidak menghadiri kelas dan pulang ke rumah. Kemudian, dia bertemu pula dengan Haryati yang telah mengubahnya menjadi manusia yang lebih baik.

programme.title: Nadia
programme.desc: Nadia mengikut ayahnya yang baru bersara daripada menjadi pegawai kedutaan Malaysia di London pulang ke Malaysia. Namun ibunya enggan pulang dan masih tinggal di London. Nadia memulakan pengajiannya di ITM dan menjalin persahabatan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Izam. Apabila Nadia mendapati ayahnya mempunyai hubungan intim dengan seorang janda kaya, dia berikrar untuk mengambil ibunya kembali serta memulihkan hubungan keluarganya yang terputus itu.

programme.title: Scoop
programme.desc: Tania, seorang wartawan menjalankan penyiasatan tentang kes pembunuhan rakannya, Johari yang menyiasat skandal syarikat kewangan. Skandal tersebut melibatkan bapa Sheila. Dibantu oleh seorang jurufoto, Norman yang ingin membersihkan namanya kerana sebelum Johari mati dibunuh, terdapat pertengkaran antara mereka berdua. Mereka pun mula menyiasat punca sebenar pembunuhan Johari.

programme.title: Kanta Serigala
programme.desc: Seorang gadis dengan impian yang besar diperkosa dan dibunuh. Shakira ingin menjadi seorang penyanyi yang terkenal kerana terpengaruh dengan penyanyi rock terkenal, Dania. Namun, malang menimpanya apabila dia telah dibunuh dua lelaki. Terkesan dengan kematian adiknya, Zarul ingin mencari pembunuh Shakira. Zarul memulakan misi untuk membalas dendam kematian adik kesayangannya.

programme.title: Siapa Dia
programme.desc: Jasmin ialah seorang guru gimnastik kolej yang sangat terkenal dan disukai ramai jejaka. Saiful cintakan Jasmin manakala Sulaiman, jaguh dalam sukan taekwondo turut menyukainya. Dikacau oleh Frankie, seorang lelaki misteri telah menyelamatkan Jasmin. Ingin mencari lelaki misteri ini, Sulaiman dan Saiful keduanya mengaku menjadi lelaki tersebut - satu pertandingan diadakan untuk menentukan pemenangnya.

programme.title: Gila Gila Pengantin Remaja
programme.desc: Pasangan remaja yang bakal menduduki peperiksaan SPM, Amir dan Mastura berikrar ingin berkahwin selepas tamatnya pengajian di universiti. Namun, Fandi yang juga rakan sekelas Mastura mencemburui percintaan mereka. SPM pun tiba tetapi Mastura terlewat menghadiri ujian Matematik dan berasa amat kecewa kerana menganggap dia telah pun gagal. Kakak Mastura, Anita pula ingin Mastura mencari calon suami yang kaya. Perasaan kecewa mula menyelubungi diri Amir apabila mendapat tahu Mastura ditunangkan dengan Fandi. Mengetahui perihal sebenar mengapa mereka akan dikahwinkan, Amir membawa Mastura lari ke selatan Thailand. Bermulalah kekecohan antara mereka semua dalam sekuel kepada Gila-Gila Pengantin ini.

programme.title: Hanny
programme.desc: Cinta Hanny dan Jeff dihalang oleh ayahnya, Dato' Mansor. Hanny pulang ke kampung bapanya dan ditunangkan dengan Faizal. Jeff memberontak dan hidup sendiri dengan mengambil upah membawa teksi setelah keluar daripada rumahnya apabila Dato' Mansor ingin menjodohkannya dengan Maria.Sofea yang juga kakak kepada Jeff telah mengupah seorang wanita bernama Sheila untuk mengintip perhubungan Jeff dan Hanny dan merosakkan hubungan mereka. Apakah kesudahan hubungan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Amelia
programme.desc: Amelia menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fandy setelah mereka bertemu secara tidak sengaja di Cameron Highlands. Dalam masa yang sama ibu Amelia ingin menjodohkannya dengan Jefri. Amelia enggan menurut kehendak ibunya kerana Jefri seorang kaki perempuan. Bapa Amelia juga menentang keputusan itu dan bertemu Fandy untuk menceritakan segala yang berlaku. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

Zulaikha kemudian bertemu Mikhail, lelaki baik hati yang sentiasa menyokongnya. Sementara itu, Yusuf meneruskan kerjayanya sebagai pelumba basikal profesional dan jatuh cinta dengan seorang wartawan sukan bernama Alya. Namun apabila Mikhail melamar Zulaikha, Yusuf mula cemburu. Mampukah Yusuf melupakan Zulaikha?

programme.title: Ruang Temu Ep63
programme.desc: Program temu bual bersama Tony Eusoff yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi beliau berkaitan pengalaman beliau di dalam industri seni

programme.title: Daddyku Gangster
programme.desc: Ray ialah ketua kumpulan yang mencuri kereta mewah dan terlibat dalam kelab pertarungan haram. Hubungannya dengan keluarga tidak baik, namun apabila abangnya Remy dan isteri Remy meninggal dunia dalam kemalangan tragis, Ray terkejut apabila mengetahui abangnya telah menamakan dia sebagai penjaga kepada dua anak mereka Arisha dan Aidil.

programme.title: Nasi Tangas (Nasi Kangkang)
programme.desc: Amira menggunakan ilmu hitam nasi tangas untuk memastikan suaminya, Remy, terus setia kepadanya. Namun perbuatan itu membawa padah apabila kehidupan mereka mula diganggu oleh kejadian mistik dan balasan akibat perbuatannya sendiri.

programme.title: Reaksiar Ep19
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Istanbul Aku Datang
programme.desc: Seorang gadis muda dari Malaysia pergi ke Istanbul untuk bertemu dengan teman lelaki kesayangannya, namun gadis yang naif itu tidak tahu apa yang akan berlaku kepada kehidupannya di sana.

programme.title: Oppa
programme.desc: Menggambarkan seorang guru yang terperangkap dalam penipuan percintaan dalam talian, mendedahkan cabaran jenayah siber di Malaysia. Usaha pihak Polis Diraja memburu penjenayah menambah elemen suspen.

programme.title: Nada Siar Ep63
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Rampok
programme.desc: Seorang wanita bersenjata memasuki sebuah bank untuk merompak. Semua orang dijadikan tebusan, dan CCTV dimatikan. Inspektor Natasya mengetuai pasukan polis tiba untuk berunding dengan perompak tersebut. Setelah rundingan berjalan lancar, tiga tebusan dibebaskan. Namun, polis tidak sedar bahawa salah seorang yang dilepaskan adalah rakan kongsi perompak itu sendiri. Perompak itu mempunyai latar belakang atau kisah peribadi yang sangat kuat yang membuatkan dia terpaksa memilih jalan merompak. Apakah rahsia sebenar di sebalik tindakan mereka?

programme.title: Abang Lejen
programme.desc: Dua beradik yang kehilangan ibu bapa mereka sejak kecil. Si abang sanggup mempertaruhkan nyawanya demi melindungi adiknya walau apa pun yang terjadi.

programme.title: Hayya 1: The Power Of Love
programme.desc: Rahmat, wartawan yang dihantui dosa silam, berhijrah jadi relawan di kem pelarian Palestin dan bertemu Hayya, anak yatim piatu. Pertemuan itu mengubah hidupnya, namun bila dia pulang ke Indonesia untuk berkahwin dengan Yasna, tercetus konflik emosi yang rumit, lucu dan tegang antara mereka.

programme.title: Hayya 2: Dream Hope And Reality
programme.desc: Filem sekuel ini menyorot trauma dan kehilangan. Hayya melarikan diri ke Indonesia lalu bertemu Lia dan Faisal, yang akhirnya menganggapnya sebagai pengikat rumah tangga mereka. Sementara Rahmat, Adhin dan Ricis terus mencarinya, rahsia keluarga Faisal terbongkar hingga tragedi besar berlaku.

programme.title: Girl In The Bunker
programme.desc: Kisah benar tentang Elizabeth Shoaf, remaja 14 tahun yang diculik lelaki menyamar sebagai polis dan dikurung dalam bunker bawah tanah. Dengan keberanian dan kepintarannya, dia berjaya menipu penculik hingga akhirnya diselamatkan

programme.title: Tukul Arwana One Man Show S1 Ep54
programme.desc: Sebuah program bual bicara yang dihoskan Tukul Arwana di Indosiar menyajikan hiburan terbaru yang akan menemani penonton semasa pandemik COVID-19 bersama bintang jemputan, tokoh masyarakat dan mereka yang tular di media sosial.

programme.title: Bumiku Lampung S1 Ep15
programme.desc: Sebuah program dokumentari yang meneroka keindahan dan kekayaan Lampung dengan sejuta kisah dalam alam semula jadi, budaya, kulinari dan kreativiti.

programme.title: Nggak Espek Mba Jamu Pelukable Banget
programme.desc: Dewi, seorang penjual jamu keliling, disukai ramai penduduk kampung kerana kecantikannya dan sikapnya yang baik hati. Suatu hari, ketika sedang berniaga, Dewi bertemu dengan seorang lelaki bernama Reno. Dewi terkejut apabila melihat Reno terdampar di sungai, dan lebih terkejut lagi apabila mengetahui Reno masih hidup. Dia segera menolong Reno, dan sejak itu hubungan mereka semakin rapat. Namun, lelaki yang menyukai Dewi tidak senang melihat keakraban mereka. Apakah yang akan terjadi seterusnya?

programme.title: Konser Luar Biasa Anak Jaman Now S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Konser Luar Biasa - Dangdut Anak Jaman Now merupakan sebuah persembahan muzik penuh warna yang menghimpunkan bintang-bintang muda dangdut paling popular masa kini. Dengan konsep pentas yang segar, koreografi bertenaga dan lagu-lagu hits terkini, konsert ini menangkap semangat generasi baharu sambil tetap mengekalkan akar tradisi dangdut.

programme.title: My Heart S1 Ep72
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Lepoq Keq Tanjung Selor S1 Ep51
programme.desc: Lepoq Keq Tanjung Selor adalah sebuah dokumentari yang meneroka keindahan alam, landskap menawan, dan tradisi unik di Tanjung Selor, Kalimantan Utara.

programme.title: Bidadari Surgamu S1 Ep448
programme.desc: Menceritakan kisah seorang gadis bernama Sakinah yang menjalani kehidupan penuh tekanan akibat fitnah dan dipaksa untuk berkahwin dengan seseorang yang tidak mencintainya. Tidak hanya itu, Sakinah juga dihalang untuk mengetahui siapa ibu kandungnya yang tega membuangnya.

programme.title: Mahkotamu Ketinggalan di DC Cakung Queen
programme.desc: Keyla terkejut apabila bertemu Roy di pasar. Roy juga tidak sengaja melihat Keyla, menyebabkan Keyla berlari masuk ke dalam pasar dan tidak sengaja bertembung dengan Yudi. Buah-buahan yang dibawa Yudi menjadi bersepah. Keyla terburu-buru mengelak daripada Roy dan terus melarikan diri. Sementara itu, Keyla sedang berusaha mencari keluarganya yang telah lama terpisah.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan peserta bertanding dalam pelbagai cabaran dalam satu permainan air, dengan impian memenangi hadiah utama.

programme.desc: Kisah ini berkisar tentang seorang gadis cantik bernama Tiara. Tiara tidak serius dalam pelajarannya semasa di universiti, menyebabkan orang tuanya marah. Akibatnya, dia dihantar ke kampung neneknya untuk menguruskan ikan lele. Di kampung tersebut, Tiara perlu menyesuaikan diri dengan persekitaran baru dan juga berdepan dengan seorang lelaki yang menyebalkan bernama Jaya. Jaya sering membuat Tiara kesal, namun dia mendapat sokongan daripada nenek Tiara. Namun, secara tiba-tiba, Tiara mula menyukai Jaya. Apa yang menyebabkan Tiara jatuh hati kepada Jaya?

programme.title: MuMu
programme.desc: Mumu, a cheerful seven-year-old girl, lives with her deaf father in a deaf community and connects him to the outside world. However, their peaceful life is disrupted when her estranged mother reappears, pushing Mumu into the hearing world. Meanwhile, her father becomes ensnared by a gang that exploits the deaf to commit crimes.

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: The White Storm 3 Heaven Or Hell
programme.desc: Hong Kong cop Billy works undercover in Suchat's drug cartel, while another undercover cop Wing successfully earns their trust in an incident and a brotherly bond is built among the three. When the police busts the syndicate, Suchat flees to the Golden Triangle with Billy and receives a tip-off about the betrayal within his circle of trust

programme.title: Undercover Hidden Dragon
programme.desc: In this hilarious comedy, Fat is a gangster who suffers from amnesia. Believing that he is actually an undercover policeman, Fat attempts to arrest gang leader Big Bro, but instead becomes the gangsters' best ally. To complicate matters further, a gangster named Wind, who looks exactly like Fat, starts a turf war with Big Bro.

programme.title: Burning Blood
programme.desc: Narcotics squad membersTai Hua, Lao Mi, Ah Feng, and Ah Tangare involved in arresting a drug lord. However, a betrayal within the police leads to the deaths of Ah Feng and his superior, while Ah Tang vanishes. As Tai Hua and Lao Mi uncover the truth, they find themselves torn between loyalty and betrayal in their fight against the drug cartel. .

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: I Fine Thank You Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Social Distancing
programme.desc: Cherry is a young girl addicted to the internet. After seeing a warning video about an e-ghost on YouTube, she begins to encounter many mysterious incidents, and the e-ghost also takes control of her family. Cherry must face her unbearable past in order to get out of this horrifying paranormal world...

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the club's top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Unbeatable
programme.desc: Former world champion boxer Fai meets fiery young fighter Qi in Macau. As he mentors Qi for an upcoming MMA tournament, Fai rekindles his passion for fighting, life, and the people he cares about.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: The Fierce Wife
programme.desc: An Zhen divorces her husband after his infidelity but faces a pivotal decision four years later - to return to her cheating husband and old life or to embark on a new life with a new love?

programme.title: The Grey Men
programme.desc: Hong Kong police officer Ah Shan goes undercover in prison to gain the trust of criminal Tian, in order to seek evidence against his gang. After their release from jail, Shan helps Tian rise within the gang and become the new boss. However, just as Shan successfully cracks down on the gang, he uncovers a shocking secret about Tian...

programme.title: Hk Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her team's performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chan's help.

programme.title: Hello Stranger
programme.desc: This is a Thai romantic comedy. The story portrays a young Thai man and woman who meet by coincidence while on vacation in South Korea. They decide to tour the country together while keeping their names a secret from each other. From unwillingly at first, then become best friends and fall in love finally.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the 'Hand of God'?

programme.title: Love Punch
programme.desc: Talented boxer Jia Yang is caught in an underground fight to clear her father's debts. She loses her Olympic aspiration and vanishes from the boxing world. 10 years later, Coach Li Yue is determined to help her honour her father's wish by returning to the ring. As passion and obligation collide, can Jia Yang revive her abandoned boxing dream?

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home, an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death, the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Operation Bangkok
programme.desc: Military veteran Wu and undercover cop Ming rescue hostages on an island near Bangkok. Just as the mission is completed and they prepare to leave, Wu discovers his daughter has also been captured. Determined to save her, he stays with Ming to fight the thugs and rescue her.

programme.title: Beauty And The 7 Beasts
programme.desc: Teddy, once a renowned movie star, is facing a career decline. To make a living, he accepts five disciples to shape them into stars. Teddy's career regains momentum after he reunites with his long-lost daughter, but he is also confronted by a rival at the same time. His daughter and disciples decide to help him overcome this difficult situation

programme.title: Ride On
programme.desc: Master Luo, a washed-up stuntman, trains his beloved horse Red Hare to be a stunt horse. Due to his debts though, Red Hare may be taken away by the debtors. Master Luo has no choice but to seek help from his estranged daughter, and the incident ends up becoming a golden opportunity for them to reconcile.

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Crisis Negotiators
programme.desc: Negotiator Wai becomes the prime suspect in a police murder case. He takes hostages at the police station and demands to negotiate with former negotiator Jun. As the two engage in a high-stake battle of wits, their expertise in psychological manipulation leads to a tense verbal sparring match, gradually shifting their positions and mind sets.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: Yu Lou is betrayed by his wife and eventually killed by her lover, Fung, who is the boss of a martial arts school. Yu Lou's brother, Xiao Lou, knows about his tragic death and is determined to take revenge for him.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tian's rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tian's granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: A dying master dispatches his last pupil to track down five ex-students who are each an expert in his own lethal combat style. He fears they will steal the fortune belonging to their clan and tasks his pupil to prevent their attempt.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They fall into a misunderstanding on the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to get her to act as his fianc so as to drive away two women whom he does not like

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: Jiang Xiao Yu is separated from his twin brother as a baby after his parents are murdered. He is taken by a couple to Villains Valley and raised to be a villain by a host of outlaws. Jiang leaves the valley to explore the world when he grows up. Will he be able to avenge his parents and meet with his twin brother?

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70's Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sister's magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Protectors
programme.desc: Ling Hsiao and Kuan Wang Lung are two guard chiefs working for an old convoy master. Lung is secretly in love with Fang Yen, the master's granddaughter but Yen is attracted to Ling Hsiao instead. In order to win her back, Lung sets up a trap to steal the convoy and frames Ling Hsiao for it.

programme.title: Killer Clans
programme.desc: This intriguing wuxia saga is packed with conspiracies, power schemes and sword fights to produce a perfect blend of great action and gripping drama. The movie centres around the struggle for underworld supremacy between two clans, where the line between good and evil is not always that clear-cut.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jin's daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: Full Moon Scimitar
programme.desc: Swordsman Ding fought against many swordsmen and won, so he took his first defeat badly and wanted to commit suicide. It is then that he meets the granddaughter of a mystic Sect leader and falls in love. When they want to get married, the Sect leader presents Ding with the Full Moon Scimitar, on the condition that he will never leave the sect.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: Life Gamble
programme.desc: Martial arts master Yu has retired for years but is invited to join force with another master Tao to fight against the four famous thieves and retrieve the stolen Dragon Jade. However, Tao's real plan is to possess the treasure himself and kills Yu after he defeats the thieves...

programme.title: Till the End of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: The Twelve Gold Medallions
programme.desc: This was one of top three films of 1970 and winner of "Outstanding Drama" at the 9th Golden Horse Awards. The evil minister uses twelve golden medallions to summon war hero Yueh Fei back from the frontline and execute him. A group of wandering warriors, led by Yueh Hua and Chin Ping, try to stop the medallion couriers.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: When Jianying discovers the Zhao clan's fortune will be left to his brother Yulong, he engineers his parents' death and sends his own son out to kill Yulong.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bill's nieces!

programme.title: Lady Of Steel
programme.desc: A young swordswoman Fang Ying Qi sets out to join the Flying Dragon Clan in their defense against the invading Jin forces. Fang also intends to avenge the murder of her parents by bandit leader Han 20 years ago. Han has since taken on a false identity as a member of the Flying Dragon Clan and Fang must rely on her deadly sword skills to stop Han.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demon's clutches.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword master's daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace. She dies on the run and returns as a spirit to take revenge by killing the evil master, and soon vanishes after returning the sword to the emperor.

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of 'scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: Legend of the Bat
programme.desc: It is rumoured that people can buy anything they desire on the mysterious Island of Bats so long as they have money. The charismatic swordsman Chu Liu Xiang and his friend travel to the island to seek answers but realize they are not the only ones who want to unveil the mystery of this place.

programme.title: The Sword Stained with Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yong's novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: The Enchanting Ghost
programme.desc: It is love beyond the grave, as a young scholar and his beautiful lover are torn apart forever by his dastardly uncle and his friend, who drive the girl to commit suicide... but with death comes revenge for the enchanting ghost. A spooky yet heart-wrenching tale...

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynasty's Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: Inside The Forbidden City
programme.desc: Justice Bao discovers that Consort Li's new born son was swapped at birth and that she was expelled from the palace by Empress Liu twenty years ago. He sets Eunuch Guo up to confess his conspiracy with the Empress. Empress Liu is convicted for her act and Consort Li finally reunites with her son who is now the Emperor.

programme.title: The Magnificent Ruffians
programme.desc: A gang of unemployed martial artists seem to have their bad fortunes turned when the head of a local security agency hires them to take out the competition, who their new employer insists is up to no good. However, the men are being played for fools and have to take each other on until the last drop of blood is spilled.

programme.title: The Cave of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brother's Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang is trapped by seven seductive spider spirits who are hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing have to fight the spider spirits to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Rape of the Sword
programme.desc: The film starts out with two students fighting for their deceased master's sword called the "Green Frost Sword". Han kills the other student, takes the sword and offer it to the king. The wife of the other dead student plots to take revenge, going undercover to retrieve the sword at the first opportunity in this tale of revenge and betrayal.

The European-style tsundere loli and Japanese-style horror cool-dere twin sister secretaries. The treasurer, who looks like an elementary school student, but is a genius hacker. programme.title: DocFilm
programme.desc: Power of Secret Service - Intelligence agencies are influencing governments and spying on countries with no regard for the law. And they are able to remain nearly invisible, in the process. Are they the new superpowers? The last time intelligence agencies commanded as much power as they do today was during the Cold War. Technological innovations mean that more sophisticated warfare is now a reality. It is not just about Russia and the USA anymore. We may be entering a new era of unrest. The U.S. has lost more spies and informants since 2010 than at any other time since the Cold War. Leaders of German intelligence agencies also acknowledge that they have once again fallen upon tough times. Money, data and access are proving to be major factors in determining who actually wields power. The 2016 U.S. election made this clear: U.S. intelligence agencies are certain that Russian intelligence helped elect Donald Trump. But the U.S. has lost old spheres of influence and allies are increasingly pursuing their own agendas. Can President Biden make his country a force for order in the world, again? And what does that mean for political hot spots and potential conflicts with China, Iran, and Russia? And for allies like Saudi Arabia and Turkey? Will Western intelligence agencies regain the power they once exerted? Wars fought with drone and hacker attacks, increasingly delegated power, and surveillance could push these conflicts to their tipping point.
